{"tid":118762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角大廈墮石屎 擊傷過路男","createTime":"2017-02-13T08:51:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T09:19:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ba9892cfe4447f1db10a5da5c34172a076159628","tid":118762,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:51:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170213/19926987\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170213%2F19926987&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklEljA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=5aa25850\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170213%2F19926987&h=154eeb47\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170213/19926987</a><br />\n<br />\n旺角大廈墮石屎<br />\n擊傷過路男<br />\n<br />\n5,945<br />\nInitial ImagePlay Button Image<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】旺角發生墮物傷人意外，荔枝角道125號大廈進行維修工程，外牆搭建棚架，昨日凌晨零時許，一名姓黃68歲男子途經上址時，疑有石屎從高處墮下，其中一塊約2、3吋直徑的石屎，打穿約15呎高棚架上的帆布，再擊中男子後腦，登時受傷流血，幸仍然清醒。救護員到場替傷者包紮送院。警方封閉大廈對開一段道路。<br />\n<br />\n另外，約同一時間油麻地寧波街與廟街交界，兩塊磚頭從高處墮下。7分鐘後油麻地砵蘭街78號亦有高空墮玻璃樽，幸沒釀成傷人事故。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n醫療物資棄街　紅會被誤大嘥鬼<br />\n下一則<br />\n醉情侶會所飲酒　疑情變街頭互毆"},{"pid":"d7841c43908a43b11432afd9c2e6753eb496c511","tid":118762,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:11:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/video/20170213/org/1486928378_3538.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20170213%2Forg%2F1486928378_3538.jpg&h=d25486be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"daaf9cecbb63a0e795e7b232762724fe0d0685a9","tid":118762,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:19:32.000Z","msg":"嘩屌我屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}